sentences: Håvard Jørgensen (born 26 September 1975), also known as Haavard, Lemarchand, is a songwriter, guitarist and vocalist.
One of the initiators of the band Eczema (which later on became Satyricon) which started up in 1991.
Eczema won (as the first death metal-act) the Oslo Championship of Rock in 1992 – and changed thereafter the name to Satyricon.
Jørgensen participated on the first demo The Forest Is My Throne, but quit the band to join the newly founded Ulver in 1993.
Jørgensen was with Ulver from 1993 to 2000, and later as a session-guitarist.
